673
01:10:59,800 --> 01:11:14,800
Yes. It's something. Yes. And so so that made you know, it could leave us though with a very depressing sort of conclusion that what Marx did was this extraordinary analysis of capitalism.

674
01:11:14,800 --> 01:11:23,800
